title: ADLIB BIBLE - RUCKMAN
description:
Dr. Ruckman's famous Ad-Lib Commentary on the Bible recorded in the 1970's. 

Old Testament - Volume 1 - From the Creation to the reign of King Saul. 18 hours, 35 

minutes. By Dr. Peter S. Ruckman

Old Testament - Volume 2 - From King Saul to the end of the Old Testament. 18 hours, 

46 minutes. By Dr. Peter S. Ruckman.

New Testament - From the shepherds in the field to "Even so, come, Lord Jesus." 21 

hours, 47 minutes. By Dr. Peter S. Ruckman


Buy it at http://store.kjv1611.org/the-ad-lib-commentary-mp3/
